    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This Porsche Cayman S (987.2) features the coveted 3.4L MA1.21 flat-six engine, utilizing Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) to eliminate IMS bearing concerns found in earlier generations. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, this mid-engine platform is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory mechanical limited-slip differential for superior cornering kinematics. The vehicle exhibits a linear power band and a 7,500 RPM redline, maintained with strict adherence to service intervals. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight with no vacuum leaks or bore scoring issues. A superlative driver's spec for those prioritizing mechanical purity and chassis balance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
