      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a pristine showpiece and a reliable daily driver. The exterior retains its deep luster, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use you\u2019d expect from a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is supple, the dash is free of cracks, and every button and dial functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it\u2019s in excellent health, having benefited from a strict maintenance schedule that ensures a smooth, responsive ride with no hidden surprises or leaks. It is a turn-key example that offers immediate enjoyment and pride of ownership without the need for immediate repairs.",
